body:
It came absolutely out of nowhere, cheated out of my hard-worked victory by a troll &quot;smurf&quot; team. I was nothing short of pissed during the end game chat. Especially when my team started begging for honors for &quot;letting them win&quot;

I know it&#039;s Normals and I shouldn&#039;t give a crap about them, but when I don&#039;t play ranked anymore, I have nowhere else to go. I would have gotten out of a losing streak and earned my first win of the day.

It&#039;s this kind of thing that makes me want to just stop playing the game, when my own team will steal my victory from me.
